{"parse":{"title":"Raw Sagefish","pageid":59927,"wikitext":{"*":"<onlyinclude>{{{{{tpl|tooltip}}}\n|mode={{{mode|}}}\n|arg={{{arg|}}}\n|sell={{cost|||25}}\n|icon=INV_Misc_Fish_20\n|quality=Common\n|itemid=21071\n|charges=1\n|ilvl=20\n|name=Raw Sagefish\n|level=10\n|effect=Use: Restores 155 health and 315 mana over 21 sec.  Must remain seated while eating.}}</onlyinclude>\n\n==Source==\nRaw Sagefish can be caught in [[Ashenvale]], [[Hillsbrad Foothills]], [[Loch Modan]], [[Silverpine Forest]] and [[Stonetalon Mountains]].\n\n==Raw Sagefish as an ingredient==\nThis item is used to make: \n* {{loot|Common|Smoked Sagefish}}\n\n==External links==\n<!-- Read http://www.wowwiki.com/WoWWiki:External_links before posting your links here.\nLinks that do not conform to the rules will be DELETED.\nRepeat violations may result in a BAN.\nHave a nice day. :) -->\n{{elinks-item|21071}}\n{{Elink|link=http://www.elsanglin.com/fish/raw_sagefish.html |site=El's Extreme Anglin' |icon=elsanglin}}\n\n[[Category:World of Warcraft common items]]\n[[Category:World of Warcraft food items]]\n[[Category:Fish]]"}}}